CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 3, 1962, pg. 16 reads: "Registration Team - There are many members of the NAACP "Get-out-The-Vote," team. The left photo shows one of the members Elizabeth Taylor in action talking with (left to right): General J. Smith Jr., Miss Ruth J. Smith, General J. Smith III, Lyndora Smith..."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of  Elizabeth Taylor, registering voters, from left: General J. Smith Jr., holding Ruth J. Smith; Lyndora Smith, and General J. Smith III, gathered in domestic interior with round mirror and dancer decoration on wall, radio in background
